item.name: Local client API

request.description: Shows list of profiles launched on your PC. webSocketDebuggerUrl will be shown only for profiles that are launched in headless mode.

For now only `headless=true` enable automation port.

This behavior will be changed in the next release and you will be able to enable automation for GUI profiles too.

item.description: Local client API to run profiles default server port is 58888 API url is http://localhost:5888
